    "body": "BIP8 has not had significant updates since 2021, but continues to be relevant. E.g., the BIP110 activation appears to have been modeled on BIP8, and the Speedy Trial activation of Taproot was implemented based on BIP8.\r\n\r\nI therefore posit that BIP8 should be advanced to Complete rather being in Draft status.\r\n\r\ncc: @btcdrak, @luke-jr as the BIP owners, but anyone’s review is welcome.",
